You can simply ask Alexa to control your space sterilizer. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our "DH Lifelabs" app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in our "DH Lifelabs" app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4) Search “DH Lifelabs” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5) Enable “DH Lifelabs” skill, and you'll be navigated to “DH Lifelabs” login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the HOCL space sterilizer.”
“Alexa, turn off the HOCL space sterilizer.”
“Alexa, turn on the Dual-Plasma space sterilizer.”
“Alexa, turn off the Dual-Plasma space sterilizer.”
